# D11 (docs/decisions.md): binary media/preset content goes through git-lfs from here on,
# so the repo's normal history stays cheap to clone even as presets/ grows. Existing large blobs
# already in history (fluidr3-gm-small.sf2, muldjordkit-small.sf2, upright-piano-kw-small.sf2)
# are NOT retroactively migrated — that needs a history rewrite, a call for the owner, not this.
*.sf2 filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.sf3 filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.wav filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.h2drumkit filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
